Created 1.4.1936 out of the parish of Winlaton. See also Table

Abolished 1.4.1937 and added to the parish of Blaydon. See

Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the Gateshead unparished 
    area. See also Table 2, note (g).

Created 1894 from the part of the parish of Heworth in Gateshead 
    County Borough. Abolished 1.4.1907 and added to the parish of Gateshead.

That part which until 1.10.1901 formed part of the parish of Chopwell. 
    See also Table 2, note (c).
Abolished 1.4.1914 and added to the parish of Ryton.

That part which until 1.4.1937 formed parts of the parishes of 
    Blaydon and Whickham. See also Table 2, note (f).
Abolished 1.4.1937 and added to the parish of Blaydon.

Abolished 1.4.1936 and divided between the parishes of Blaydon, 
    Whickham and Stanley.
